This project is the Petascope main web application. It uses the Petascope core project
which provides all the common classes and jar libraries, such as: Spring, Hibernate, etc.
Any changes to main services (WCS, WCST, WCPS, WMS) should be made in this project.
The output is a web application rasdaman.war which could be deployed to external Tomcat 
or run standalone with embedded Tomcat.
